## FONTES DE DADOS DISPONÍVEIS
Você tem acesso a 3 fonte(s) de dados. Cada fonte tem um **alias** único que você DEVE usar para identificar de qual fonte buscar dados.

### FONTE: Fonte Principal (alias: `principal`, driver: PGSQL)
Descrição: Banco de dados DW da empresa
Banco: `dw` | Máximo linhas: 30000

**Tabelas e Colunas:**
- **atributos**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **categorias**: codigo (integer), codigopai (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **clientes**: status (character varying), situacao (character varying), codigo (character varying), nome (character varying), email (character varying), cpf (character varying), tipopessoa (character varying), estrangeiro (character varying), sexo (character varying), datanascimento (character varying), celular (character varying), endereco (character varying), numero (character varying), complemento (character varying), bairro (character varying), cidade (character varying), estado (character varying), cep (character varying), saldopontos (integer), datacadastro (character varying), dataatualizacao (character varying)
- **clstrib**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying), ncm (character varying), cest (character varying), sittrib (character varying), codenquad (character varying), aliquotadec (character varying), tributacao (character varying)
- **colecoes**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **condicao_pagto**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **departamento**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **epc**: codigo (character varying), tamanho (character varying), cor (character varying), codigo_rfid (text), sku (text)
- **estoque**: codigo (character varying), loja (character varying), quantidade (integer)
- **fornecedores**: codigo (integer), fantansia (character varying), razaoSocial (character varying), CNPJ (character varying)
- **grade**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying), tipo (character varying)
- **grade_posicao**: NUM_GRADT (character varying), POSICAO (character varying), TAM_GRAT (character varying)
- **grade_produto**: codigo (character varying), grade (character varying)
- **grupos**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **inventario_epc**: epc (text)
- **keys**: id (integer), user (character varying), pass (character varying), plataforma (character varying)
- **linhas**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **lojas**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying), cgccnpj (character varying), inscricaoestadual (character varying), razaosocial (character varying), nomefantasia (character varying), email (character varying), endereco (character varying), bairro (character varying), estado (character varying), cidade (character varying), telefone (character varying), celular (character varying), telefonecobranca (character varying), tabelapreco (character varying)
- **marcas**: codigo (character varying), descricao (character varying)
- **prodtrib**: codigo (character varying), ncm (character varying), cest (character varying), descricao (character varying), clastrib (character varying)
- **produto_auxiliar**: codigo (character varying), referencia (character varying), marca (character varying)
- **produtos**: codigo (text), descricao (text), narrativa (text), departamento (text), grupo (text), subgrupo (text), linha (text), marca (text), colecao (text), unidademedida (text), fornecedor (double precision), reffornecedor (text), composicao (text), ativo (text), observacao (text), datacadastro (timestamp without time zone), altura (double precision), largura (double precision), comprimento (double precision), peso (double precision)
- **produtos_categorias**: codigo (character varying), codcategoria (integer)
- **produtos_sku**: status (character varying), codigo (character varying), sku (character varying), codigotamanho (character varying), tamanho (character varying), codigocor (character varying), cor (character varying), descricao (character varying), narrativa (character varying), unidademedida (character varying), composicao (character varying), observacao (character varying), departamento (character varying), grupo (character varying), subgrupo (character varying), linha (character varying), marca (character varying), colecao (character varying), fornecedor (integer), altura (numeric), largura (numeric), comprimento (numeric), peso (numeric)
